column2: SELECT p.photoRa, p.photoDec, p.z, p.zerr, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr FROM SpecObj as s JOIN SpecPhotoAll as p on s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.ra between # and # AND p.dec between # and # AND p.class=&&& AND (p.petroMag_r-p.extinction_r) < # and p.zwarning = # AND p.survey = &&& and p.programname = &&& AND p.subclass=&&&
